metadata.name: Electric Drift
metadata.description:
A groundbreaking multi-layered music video experience. Experimental sound design paired with real lasers and augmented reality.

My song was sent to Laser Lew Dude ( https://twitter.com/laser_lew ) and he worked his magick. The visuals were created using his real lasers synchronized to my music.

Every collector will get a signed print that activates the full music video in AR.
